You're listening to Dirt Sheet Radio!!

WrestleMania in Saudi Arabia?? The inevitable has arrived.

TKO's business moves have begun rubbing fans the wrong way. Is this cause for concern or is the fanbase loyal enough to put rent checks towards wrestling tickets?

Wardlow suffers an injury immediately after his return from a year plus absence. Is this the end?

AJ Lee returns to the WWE after 11 years for a multi year run! What does her future look like in today's environment?

AJ Styles contract comes up in February 2026. Is his career coming to an end? Or is a new chapter about to begin?

AEW Dynamite Recap 09-10-2025

